oliants are soft enough to use daily, but here's the lowdown: start slow, my skincare lovers.</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Start using an exfoliant once a week. And when you think that your skin can take more, build it slowly up.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Especially when using chemical exfoliants, it's particularly important to remember to use sunscreen! Chemical exfoliants, such as BHA/PHA/AHA, make the skin more sensitive to sunlight.</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"></span></p><p><i></i></p><p><i></i></p><p><i></i></p><p><i></i></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1711459314310" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711459314310" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1707204138727" data-id="1707204138727" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: 0px;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711459314428" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711459314428"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><u style="">Apply eye masks to de-puff:</u></p><p>Our secret to having the most hydrated and smoothing eyes are under-eye eyepatches. They’re so easy to pop on while you’re doing your hair or eye makeup (to catch any eyeshadow fallout) that sometimes we even forget we have them on! We love storing them in the fridge for a cooling effect. Not only will they help you look well-rested, but they also help to prep your under-eye area for concealer.</p><p><br></p><p><u>Sealing the Deal - Moisturize:</u></p><p>When it's time to moisturize, it's like the grand finale – the moment we wrap up our skincare love story.</p><p>Grab your favorite rich moisturizer – It locks in all the good stuff and creates a protective shield. It's like giving your skin the ultimate hug, getting it ready to conquer the world.</p><p><br></p><p>Think of it as the perfect ending to a feel-good movie, where everything just falls into place. Our moisturizer is the hero that makes sure our skin is not just happy but ready to shine.</p><p>Let's lavish our skin with that moisturizer, wrap up our routine, and get ready to glow. Our skin is gonna thank us for this epic love story!</p><p><i></i></p><p><i></i></p><p><i></i></p><p><i></i></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1707204144637" data-id="1707204144637" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: 0px;"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1711459314352" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1711459314352" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="auto" style="" data-current-variant="39916406931585"><product-form class="product-form">{% assign product = all_products['propolis-vitamin-eye-cream-set-freebie'] %}{%